    8AC +3 Str +5 Dex<br><br>I've got an Ogre with a Str of 220 before any buffs and all this equipment was gained at level 30.  Course I have 4 Level 30 chars who combined money, but still...<br><br>Buy the way, If I had the money for Cobalt I would get it :P<br><br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >6 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
